snippet.title: Gynophobia Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Get it on Steam for PC and Mac: http://store.steampowered.com/app/365020/

New website: http://vintsevych.com/

Gynophobia is a horror and shooter about fear of women. 

Mark suffers from different phobias, including abnormal fear of women. At some point he will receive an opportunity to overcome his fears.
